              "options": [
                {
                  "label": "(a) Bisect the current deploy issue first",
                  "pros": "Cheapest; isolates the actual root cause; doesn't commit to a platform shift",
                  "cons": "Doesn't resolve the long-term hosting question; may surface a fix that's specific to today's symptom rather than tomorrow's class"
                },
                {
                  "label": "(b) Migrate hosted routes only",
                  "pros": "Smaller blast radius than full migration; lets us evaluate Vercel on a subset; reversible per-route",
