      {
        "node_id": "circuit-launch-sprint-2026-05-29",
        "parent_id": "root-sprint",
        "title": "2026-05-29 One Season launch sprint",
        "tree_id": "global",
        "state": "open",
        "items": [
          {
            "item_id": "cls-s1",
            "kind": "action",
            "text": "S1 Auth & Access (P0): login/forgot-password repair, Google sign-in + post-invite refresh bug, \"you already exist\" re-invite block, bulk invite 1-of-4 � C-07/C-08/C-47/C-31",
            "checked": false,
            "deferred": false,
            "scheduled_for": null,
            "contested": null
          },
          {
            "item_id": "cls-s2",
            "kind": "action",
            "text": "S2 Org Form Hardening (P0): Industry+Timezone dropdowns on /admin/orgs, hide slug field, jsdom+RTL component-test infra � WALKTHROUGH-001 = C-01/C-02",
            "checked": false,
            "deferred": false,
            "scheduled_for": null,
            "contested": null
          },
          {
            "item_id": "cls-s3",
            "kind": "action",
            "text": "S3 Search/Save/Persistence (P0): fix contact search, contact-create persistence, Personal Data save no-op, member-role update, standardize save UX � C-12/C-41/C-21/C-32/C-35",
            "checked": false,
            "deferred": false,
            "scheduled_for": null,
            "contested": null
          },
          {
            "item_id": "cls-s4",
            "kind": "action",
            "text": "S4 Contact Import Hardening (P0): address mapping, full-name split, per-row error reporting, phone + prefix � C-15/C-10/C-11/C-16 (overlaps S3 contact pages)",
            "checked": false,
            "deferred": false,
            "scheduled_for": null,
            "contested": null
          },
          {
            "item_id": "cls-s5",
            "kind": "action",
            "text": "S5 CallRail Integration (P0): API scoping+wiring, RingCentral compat, demonstrable end-to-end for One Season � C-04/C-06 (biggest blocker)",
            "checked": false,
            "deferred": false,
            "scheduled_for": null,
            "contested": null
          },
          {
            "item_id": "cls-tier2",
            "kind": "action",
            "text": "Tier 2 (queued): Schedules & Availability, dynamic import auto-mapping (C-09), Comm-Prefs overhaul (C-25/26/27/28/29), AI-suggested message (C-17), test-orgs purge (C-03), misc UX bundle",
            "checked": false,
            "deferred": false,
            "scheduled_for": null,
            "contested": null
          },
          {
            "item_id": "cls-tier3",
            "kind": "action",
            "text": "Tier 3 (Architecture, Jaime): PRD draft from build doctrine + code audit, 22-contradiction guardrails ship, conversation engine principles",
            "checked": false,
            "deferred": false,
            "scheduled_for": null,
            "contested": null
          },
          {
            "item_id": "cls-coord-cody",
            "kind": "action",
            "text": "COORD � Cody: provide real contact export file (blocks S4 import verification)",
            "checked": false,
            "deferred": false,
            "scheduled_for": null,
            "contested": null
          },
          {
            "item_id": "cls-coord-jaime",
            "kind": "action",
            "text": "COORD � Jaime: ship 22-contradiction guardrails + PRD draft (Tier 3) + CallRail/RingCentral docs C-05 (blocks S5)",
            "checked": false,
            "deferred": false,
            "scheduled_for": null,
            "contested": null
          },
          {
            "item_id": "cls-coord-misha",
            "kind": "action",
            "text": "COORD � Misha: review CallRail scope before merge (S5); decide which test orgs to purge (C-03)",
            "checked": false,
            "deferred": false,
            "scheduled_for": null,
            "contested": null
          },
          {
            "item_id": "cls-dec-callrail-auth",
            "kind": "decision",
            "text": "DECIDED 2026-05-29: CallRail webhook auth = per-org unguessable URL token (matches Retell handler pattern; no HMAC because CallRail does not expose a usable signature mechanism). Documented in PR #371 scoping doc.",
            "checked": true,
            "deferred": false,
            "scheduled_for": null,
            "contested": null
          },
          {
            "item_id": "cls-dec-no-ringcentral",
            "kind": "decision",
            "text": "DECIDED 2026-05-29: RingCentral integration NOT needed � CallRail abstracts RingCentral. S5 scope reduced (C-06 dropped from S5 sub-items).",
            "checked": true,
            "deferred": false,
            "scheduled_for": null,
            "contested": null
          },
          {
            "item_id": "cls-dec-email-account-constraint",
            "kind": "decision",
            "text": "DECIDED 2026-05-29: Each email maps to ONE org + ONE user. C-47 implements as inline invite-UI warning � (a) \"this email already has an account\", (b) same-org vs different-org context with org name visible to inviter, (c) \"move account here\" affordance. No new screens.",
            "checked": true,
            "deferred": false,
            "scheduled_for": null,
            "contested": null
          },
          {
            "item_id": "cls-tier2-contact-delete",
            "kind": "action",
            "text": "Tier 2: Contact deletion/archive (verified gap � no DELETE handler at src/app/api/contacts/[id]/route.ts, bulk-action route supports only move_stage + send_message, no soft-delete fields, no UI delete button). Recommend soft-archive default. Owner-only with admin override per org policy. UI surfaces: contact detail (single), list (bulk), confirmation modal.",
            "checked": false,
            "deferred": false,
            "scheduled_for": null,
            "contested": null
          },
          {
            "item_id": "cls-s8-support-chatbot",
            "kind": "action",
            "text": "Tier 2: S8 � In-app support chatbot. Floating Help widget on every Circuit page. Phase 1 = Q&A over Support Pages MDX corpus. Phase 2 = tool-call extension (show-me-where-X-is, explain-this-error, summarize-org-state, whats-changed-recently). Uses Circuit LLM client. Per-user conversation history. Plugin interface for new tools. Was BLOCKED on S7 Phase 2 ? SHIPPED in PR #378 ? UNBLOCKED 2026-05-29.",
            "checked": false,
            "deferred": false,
            "scheduled_for": null,
            "contested": null
          },
          {
            "item_id": "cls-dec-contact-delete-shape",
            "kind": "decision",
            "text": "DECIDED 2026-05-29: Contact deletion = soft-archive ONLY on contractor surface (archived_at, hidden from list/search, reversible by admin, audit trail preserved). Hard-delete reserved for verified CCPA requests via dedicated admin-only workflow (structured request log, 24-month retention, third-party vendor notification trigger). Hard-delete NOT exposed in regular contact UI.",
            "checked": true,
            "deferred": false,
            "scheduled_for": null,
            "contested": null
          },
          {
            "item_id": "cls-hotfix-test-orgs",
            "kind": "action",
            "text": "HF-1 (Hotfix): disable test-org generation in prod. Circuit creating circuit-test* orgs daily. Session local_65df9ac4-433d-4465-9a1f-a24dfb42cdc0. 6 steps: identify source ? disable via PR ? count accumulated test orgs ? soft-archive them ? add guard against silent re-enable ? 24h regression watch.",
            "checked": false,
            "deferred": false,
            "scheduled_for": null,
            "contested": null
          },
          {
            "item_id": "cls-q-ccpa-tier",
            "kind": "question",
            "text": "OPEN (Misha decision): is the CCPA-request workflow in Tier 2 (pre-launch) or Tier 3? Circuit serves California contractors + California consumers; Misha leans Tier 2.",
            "checked": false,
            "deferred": false,
            "scheduled_for": null,
            "contested": null
          }
